sections.heading: in actions on claims not due; procedure in general
sections.text: The proceedings under general attachment provided for in sections 25-1004 to 25-1041, so far as they are applicable, shall regulate the attachments authorized on claims before due.SourceR.S.1867, Code ยง 243, p. 433;R.S.1913, ยง 7784;R.S.1922, ยง 8728;
